---
layout: base.njk
title: Tesla News & Updates
description: Latest Tesla news, model updates, buying guides, and ownership tips from Tesla DIY Repair.
---

<div class="section-header" style="margin-bottom: 2rem;">
  <h1>Tesla News & Updates</h1>
  <p>Model updates, ownership guides, buying advice, and the latest from Tesla</p>
</div>

<div class="posts-grid">
  {% for post in collections.newsItems %}
    <article class="post-card">
      <div class="post-card-visual cat-{{ post.data.category | lower | replace(' ', '-') | replace('&', '') | replace('  ', '-') }}">
        <span class="cat-icon">📰</span>
      </div>
      <div class="post-card-content">
        <div class="post-card-tags">
          {% if post.data.category %}
            <span class="post-card-category category-tag">{{ post.data.category }}</span>
          {% endif %}
        </div>
        <h3><a href="{{ post.url }}">{{ post.data.title }}</a></h3>
        <p>{{ post.data.description }}</p>
        <div class="post-card-meta">
          <span>{{ post.data.readTime or "5 min read" }}</span>
          <span class="read-more" aria-hidden="true">Read More →</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </article>
  {% endfor %}
</div>

{% if collections.newsItems | length == 0 %}
  <p style="text-align: center; padding: 3rem; color: #666;">No news articles yet.</p>
{% endif %}

<style>
  .post-card-tags {
    display: flex;
    gap: 0.5rem;
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }

  .category-tag {
    background: #e8e8e8 !important;
    color: #555 !important;
  }

  .post-card-visual {
    height: 100px;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #667eea 0%, #764ba2 100%);
  }

  .cat-icon {
    font-size: 2.5rem;
    filter: drop-shadow(0 2px 4px rgba(0,0,0,0.2));
  }

  .post-card {
    position: relative;
  }

  .post-card h3 a::after {
    content: "";
    position: absolute;
    inset: 0;
  }
</style>
